'''中国金融四十人论坛'''（{{lang-en|China Finance 40 Forum}}）是一个位于[[北京|北京]]的[[智库|智库]]。专注于[[宏观经济|宏观经济]]和金融政策研究。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1019&context=think_tanks|page=103|title=2020 Global Go To Think Tank Index Report|author=James G. McGann|date={{date|2021/01/28}}|website=University of Pennsylvania|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522000141/https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1019&context=think_tanks}}</ref>

==历史==
[[File:Former_China_Coal_Merchants'_Bank_Building.JPG|thumb]]]]
[[File:天津中法工商银行大楼.jpg|thumb]]]]

2008年4月12日成立，由40位40岁以下经济学专家。总部位于[[北京|北京]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=China's Independent Think Tanks: A Comparative Perspective |date={{date|2013/02/04}} |url=https://www8.gsb.columbia.edu/apec/archive/2013 |website=Columbia Business School APEC Study Center |access-date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214115150/https://www8.gsb.columbia.edu/apec/archive/2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |website=Peking University |url=https://en.idf.pku.edu.cn/aboutus/council1/272535.htm |title=Haiming Wang |access-date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214054551/https://en.idf.pku.edu.cn/aboutus/council1/272535.htm }}</ref>2011年建立上海新金融研究院，位于[[盐业大楼|盐业大楼]]，2016年建立北方新金融研究院，位于[[天津中法工商银行大楼|天津中法工商银行大楼]]。经常单独或合作举办各类活动，合作方诸如欧洲[[智库|智库]][[布鲁盖尔|布鲁盖尔]]<ref>{{cite web|title=China-Europe-US Economists Symposium: Reform—Challenges & Opportunities|website=Bruegel|url=https://www.bruegel.org/events/china-europe-us-economists-symposium-reform-challenges-opportunities/|date={{date|2014/05/17}}}}</ref>和美国[[智库|智库]][[彼得森国际经济研究所|彼得森国际经济研究所]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.piie.com/events/us-china-economic-relations-conflict-solutions|title=US-China Economic Relations: From Conflict to Solutions|date={{date|2018/06/11}}|website=PIIE Peterson Institute for International Economics|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204002646/https://www.piie.com/events/us-china-economic-relations-conflict-solutions}}</ref>

2019年开始在[[上海|上海]][[外滩|外滩]]主办[[外滩金融峰会|外滩金融峰会]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cf40.com/en/news_detail/11405.html|title=The 2nd Bund Summit - Crisis and Opportunities: New Finance and New Economy in a New Situation|website=CF40|date={{date|2020/10/23}}}}</ref>2020年10月24日[[阿里巴巴集团|阿里巴巴集团]]实际控制人[[马云|马云]]在第二届[[外滩金融峰会|外滩金融峰会]]上的发言直接导致[[蚂蚁集团|蚂蚁集团]]在[[上海证券交易所|上海证券交易所]]和[[香港交易所|香港交易所]]的[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]暂缓。<ref>{{citation|website=New York Times|title=In Halting Ant's I.P.O., China Sends a Warning to Business|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/06/technology/china-ant-group-ipo.html|author=Raymond Zhong|date={{date|2020/11/06}}|accessdate=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604163830/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/06/technology/china-ant-group-ipo.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |website=China Daily |url=https://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202008/31/WS5f4c41eca310675eafc56610.html |title=Financial opening-up suggested as driver of new five-year-plan |author=Chen Jia |date={{date|2020/08/31}} |access-date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214115151/https://global.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202008/31/WS5f4c41eca310675eafc56610.html }}</ref>

